When this Equipment enters, draw a card.
Equipped creature has flying.
Equip {2}

When this equipment enters, you may search your library and/or hand for three cards named Fourth Player's Key and put them onto the battlefield.
When equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, draw a card. If three other creatures equipped by cards named Fourth Player's Key also dealt combat damage to that player, you may cast up to one spell from your hand without paying its mana cost.
Equip {2}
